These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, gardening
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, architect
1. the freelancer is in an even position##4
2. the architect is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | gardening | fishing |
| Job     | architect    | freelancer   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, climbing
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | milk        |
| Sport      | soccer  | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, gospel
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, nigerian
1. the colombian is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | electronic |
| Nationality   | colombian | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, watermelon
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | fanta      | milk |
| Food       | strawberry | watermelon    |

 #################################

 
