.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, rowing
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | rowing | golf  |
| Transport   | trike  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
