The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, soccer
1. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the australian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | australian   |
| Sport         | badminton | soccer |

